SUMMARY:Stellar Spaghetti Cook Off Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:🚀🍝 STELLAR SPAGHETTI COOK OFF LAUNCHING! 🍝🚀\nPrepare for launch! The Stellar Spaghetti Cook Off is touching down on March 21st at Denali Harley-Davidson from 12PM–3PM\, and it’s going to be out of this world. 🌌\nLocal cooks will battle it out for galactic glory\, serving up their best spaghetti creations while you help decide which sauce reigns supreme. Entry fees and voting fees are all donations to Katie’s Handprint Charity\, the official charity of Spenard Bike Week\, so every bite supports an amazing cause. ❤️\n🌟 KEY DRAWING AT 3PM! 🌟\nStick around until the end — you never know when luck will align like the planets.\n👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Fun for the whole family\n👩‍🚀 Dress in your best space costume for a chance to win a grand prize\n🍝 Cosmic carbs\, saucy competition\, and stellar vibes\nBring your crew\, fuel up on spaghetti\, and help us kick off Spenard Bike Week season in true space-themed style. One small step for pasta… one giant leap for Bike Week. 👽✨\n📅 March 21\n📍 Denali Harley-Davidson\n⏰ 12PM–3PM\n🍝 Spaghetti Cook Off\n🗝️ Key Drawing at 3PM\n🚀 Space Costumes Encouraged\nThis event is going full throttle to the stars — don’t miss it!\n$20 to enter your spaghetti – donation to Katie’s Handprint\n$5 to taste and vote- donation to Katie’s Handprint\nPlease Register In Advance to bring Spaghetti! -email marketing@ harleyalaska.com or stop into Denali H-D to sign up! Spaghetti must be prepped\, hot and ready to serve onsite in a crockpot by 12PM. Please bring an extension cord!\nWinner determined by popular vote\, bring your friends and family!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/stellar-spaghetti-cook-off-fundraiser/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spaghetti-fundraiser-03.21.26.jpg
END:VEVENT
