SUMMARY:24th Annual Spaghetti Dinner & Auction
DESCRIPTION:🌟 Join us for a night filled with pasta\, fun\, laughter\, and community love! 🌟\nWe’re excited to welcome you to the 24th Annual Spaghetti Dinner & Auction benefiting Special Olympics Alaska Mat-Su Community Program!\n📅 Saturday\, March 21st\n📍 Mat-Su Career & Tech High School\n⏰ Doors open at 4:30 PM\n🍽️ Dinner served 5:00–7:00 PM\n🎉 Our one-of-a-kind $1 Auction runs 6:30–9:00 PM — don’t forget your $1 bills!\n📝 Silent & Dessert Auctions will run throughout the evening as well.\n🎟️ $15 General Admission\nIncludes a full spaghetti dinner (spaghetti\, salad\, green beans\, garlic bread\, cookie\, and beverage) and admission to all auctions.\nTickets available online or at the door — but dinner is not guaranteed for at-the-door purchases\, so grab yours early at myalaskatix.com or call 907-631-8591.\n💙 This event supports 250+ incredible Special Olympics Alaska Mat-Su athletes! It is only through the generosity of our community that we are able to continue providing year-round sports training and competitions.\nIf you would like to sponsor or donate\, please contact 907-631-8591 or message us!\nCome celebrate our athletes\, enjoy a delicious meal\, and help us continue building a stronger\, more inclusive Mat-Su!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/24th-annual-spaghetti-dinner-auction/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spaghetti-dinner-and-auction-fundraiser-3.21.26.jpg
END:VEVENT
