SUMMARY:Young Entrepreneur Expo
DESCRIPTION:The Spring Young Entrepreneur Expo is officially open for registration!\nDo you have a young creator\, maker\, or business-minded student who’s ready to share their ideas? This event allows youth to showcase products or services\, build confidence\, and gain real-world entrepreneurship experience in a fun\, supportive environment. \nWho can participate?\nElementary\, Middle School\, and High School students!\nWhere: Everett’s Restaurant at the Mat-Su Resort\nWhen: Saturday\, March 28 | 12:00–4:00 PM\nSpots are limited and have filled quickly in the past; register early!\nRegister here: https://youth-360.dreamclass.io/pages/admissions/form/kGJCzo\nPlease like\, share\, and tag families who may be interested! \n$10 entry fee or vendors\, free to shop \nThe youth vendors will be scored by a panel of judges and win exciting cash prizes.
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/young-entrepreneur-expo/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=application/pdf:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/young-entrepreneur.pdf
